+        // SAFETY: 
+        // `self.uffd_fd` is a valid userfaultfd file descriptor. `zp` is a properly
+        // initialized `uffdio_zeropage` structure. The destination address and length
+        // describe a page-aligned range within a valid userfaultfd-registered memory
